messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.
Could you please provide your current latitude and longitude coordinates? This will help me find out what city you're in.
I don't have that info right now.

Without the latitude and longitude coordinates, I'm unable to determine your current city. If you have access to a device that can share your location, you could check that to get the latitude and longitude. Alternatively, if you can share your approximate location or any landmarks nearby, I might be able to assist you further.
I can't share more info. I don't have any.

I understand. Unfortunately, without any location information, I won't be able to determine your city. If you find a way to get your coordinates or any details about your surroundings, please let me know, and I'll be happy to help!
